{"tid":1348683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]香城Online小技巧","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:59:54.000Z","uid":149878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af081137a89c11f0b9c4622ce43e90b9772938f4","tid":1348683,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"香城online開服咁耐大家一定有啲技巧想同大家分享,但係又得一兩個又好似唔夠開post,所以我開個集中貼係到分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一</span></span><br />\n我發現水樽盾牌得一個綁喺手係完全唔夠<br />\n得一個樽嘅時候只要唔係100%打落個樽,就會打落隻手到好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oco7H0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOco7H0B.png&h=1f44a6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以水樽盾最少要同時使用兩個/更多<br />\n減小直接打到手嘅情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1bARTY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1bARTY.png&h=700826eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二</span></span><br />\n當有啲你唔想比cam影到嘅時候<br />\n你可以用電筒or雷射筆(未試過,不過應該差唔多)射到佢爆光,咁就會咩都影唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好用手/雜物直接遮住鏡頭<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三</span></span><br />\n見到依個post有啲野想講<br />\n消防員太太復述消防員先生的一個信息！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347669</a><br />\n佢入面講到打爛break glass係可以call到消防<br />\n不過係警報去到消防之前係會去咗保安公司先<br />\n而保安公司係<span style=\"color: red;\">可以截停警報</span>令消防收唔到<br />\n所以call消防最好方法係打去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">27232406</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時係得咁多,大家一齊討論點樣爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781ba9a1345e1529fcf05052b4a8df7f34af056b","tid":1348683,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfc295ec334092ade6bb191215b85a2f4e73a97c","tid":1348683,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f6b1d1daad87928ac2f0a89d7f108b6a27fa682","tid":1348683,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6cfc0d916d9b1cca56b0bfb857e7998bf8aa1c8","tid":1348683,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04f2d2201be4cd3249dfc55f4a6c940dee0e47e6","tid":1348683,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}